name: Disney's Finding Nemo - The Continuing Adventures [GBA]
description:
Finding Nemo is an adventure game developed by Traveller's Tales. It was originally released in 2003. THQ published the game. Most rawgers rated the game as "Meh".
You can play Finding Nemo on Game Boy Advance, Xbox, GameCube and PlayStation 2.
It was scored by Andy Blythe and Marten Joustra.
